<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Three joining fragments of a <rs type="material" key="marmor">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">statue base</rs> (together <measure type="length" dim="none">0.51</measure>   × <measure type="length" dim="none">1.38</measure>   × <measure type="depth" dim="none">0.47</measure>) with moulded panels on all four sides. </p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p>Inscribed within the front panel; the text must have begun on a crowning feature.</p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Description of Letters</head>
<p><measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.02-0.0225</measure>. Ligatures:  <foreign lang="grc">ΜΝ</foreign>, l.8; <foreign lang="grc">ΝΗ</foreign>, l. 9; <foreign lang="grc">ΜΕ</foreign>, l.12; <foreign lang="grc">ΤΗΝ</foreign>, l.13; <foreign lang="grc">ΤΗ</foreign>, ll. 14, 18, 19; <foreign lang="grc">ΜΗ</foreign>, ll. 21, 29; <foreign lang="grc">ΝΤ</foreign> l. 25; in l. 14 final <term lang="grc-Latn">iota</term> squeezed in.</p>
</div>

